# User Authentication Spec

## Overview
The user authentication system for espasyoMLS allows real estate agents and users to securely register, login, and manage their accounts.

## Requirements
- Users must be able to register with email, password, and basic profile information.
- Passwords must be securely hashed and stored.
- Users can login using email and password.
- Implement JWT tokens for session management.
- Users can logout, invalidating their session.
- Password reset functionality via email.
- Role-based access: agents, admins, regular users.

## API Endpoints
- POST /auth/register
- POST /auth/login
- POST /auth/logout
- POST /auth/reset-password

## Security
- Use HTTPS for all communications.
- Implement rate limiting on auth endpoints.
- Validate input data.
- Use secure password policies.